Quote: To apply oneself with the utmost vigour and purpose in a short-term project. .in 4;`He played  Larry Dooley there for a while. He's reorganized that business from top to bottom. He got rid of two or three chaps that used to stand about doing nothing and everybody's got to wear white coats.' `My word, when he comes home and sees how neglected the place is, he'll play Larry Dooley. Some of those relations of his wife's will he making a quick exit - that'll be one of the first things.'
